<i>Every day, I had this image</i>
<i>in front of my eyes.</i>

23:36.333 --> 23:38.375
I was looking for you around the world.

23:41.667 --> 23:43.125
Somewhere inside me,

23:43.208 --> 23:45.250
I had this feeling of certainty that...

23:46.417 --> 23:48.958
one day you would stand in front of me
and be mine.

23:51.125 --> 23:52.542
[Laura] You must be kidding.

23:53.333 --> 23:55.750
Nobody owns me. I'm not an object.

23:58.417 --> 24:02.042
You can't have me just like that;
kidnap me and think that I'm all yours.

24:04.000 --> 24:04.833
I know.

24:06.958 --> 24:10.083
But that's why I'm giving you
a chance to fall in love with me.

24:11.458 --> 24:13.167
Not because I made you do it,

24:14.125 --> 24:15.375
because you will want to.

24:16.708 --> 24:19.042
But I've got a boyfriend
who is going to look for me.

24:19.125 --> 24:20.583
I've got family, friends...

24:20.667 --> 24:22.417
I've got my own life.

24:22.500 --> 24:24.833
I don't need a chance for love from you!

24:25.250 --> 24:28.583
So, I kindly ask you
to let me the fuck out!

24:52.917 --> 24:54.667
Your boyfriend doesn't deserve you.

24:58.375 --> 25:00.833
My people have taken your stuff
from the room...

25:02.708 --> 25:04.125
and left a note for Martin.

25:04.292 --> 25:05.167
It says that...

25:06.375 --> 25:08.625
you're coming back to Poland,
moving out...

25:10.500 --> 25:11.875
disappearing from his life.

25:13.958 --> 25:15.000
You know what?

25:15.917 --> 25:16.958
Fuck off.

25:19.375 --> 25:20.375
[grunts]

25:32.500 --> 25:34.750
I won't do anything
without your permission.

25:37.333 --> 25:38.750
I'll wait until you want me,

25:40.250 --> 25:42.292
you desire me,
and come to me yourself.

25:44.542 --> 25:45.667
I won't tie you up,

25:46.208 --> 25:47.292
but don't provoke me.

25:47.625 --> 25:48.750
I can't be gentle.

25:49.833 --> 25:52.208
I'm not used to tolerating disobedience.

25:57.292 --> 25:58.250
[sighs]

26:06.000 --> 26:07.833
You have 365 days.

26:09.917 --> 26:12.167
I'd do anything
so you can fall in love with me.

26:13.583 --> 26:16.625
If next year, on your birthday,
nothing change, I'll set you free.

26:29.875 --> 26:30.833
Okay.

26:31.708 --> 26:33.458
Now, you put down the gun...

26:34.750 --> 26:36.500
or this will be stop being funny.

26:43.375 --> 26:44.917
Do you really wanna kill me?

26:45.583 --> 26:47.708
Many have tried. It's not that easy.

26:48.250 --> 26:49.583
[in Italian] Excuse me.

26:50.417 --> 26:51.875
There's been a delivery.

26:52.667 --> 26:54.208
You need to sign.

27:02.583 --> 27:03.667
Take her to her room.

27:12.625 --> 27:13.958
[in English] Okay, let's go.

27:20.875 --> 27:23.000
[in Italian] Massimo.
There will be problems.

27:23.083 --> 27:24.792
The conflict with the Gattuso family

27:25.375 --> 27:26.750
might ruin the business.

27:27.375 --> 27:28.542
Mind your own business.

27:29.083 --> 27:34.833
