to a brothel.

29:09.417 --> 29:11.208
Did you think I wouldn't find out?

29:12.625 --> 29:15.208
-We all have skeletons in the closet--
-Shut up.

29:17.667 --> 29:19.917
You have smeared
the name of this family, Alfredo.

29:20.708 --> 29:21.542
What family?

29:22.333 --> 29:23.167
What values?

29:24.042 --> 29:25.917
Spare me this bullshit, and shoot me.

29:34.958 --> 29:36.000
You will be erased.

29:36.208 --> 29:38.292
No trace will be left of you...

29:39.250 --> 29:40.542
as if you never existed.

29:44.167 --> 29:45.667
That's your punishment.

29:54.917 --> 29:56.917
[water running]

30:27.125 --> 30:28.333
[silenced gunshot]

30:28.917 --> 30:30.500
You see those marks?

30:30.583 --> 30:32.167
-Unbelievable.
-The scumbag.

30:32.500 --> 30:34.500
